e due to server misbehaving, resulting in connection issues with emailservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"someone@example.com\\\": rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据异常指标数据分析，故障期间内出现显著变化的关键指标如下：\n\n### 异常指标\n1. **checkoutservice 服务**\n    - `error_ratio`: 正常中值 0.0 上升到故障中值 25.98。\n    - `server_error_ratio`: 正常中值 0.0 上升到故障中值 25.98。\n    - `rrt_max` (最大请求响应时间)：正常中值 162292 微秒，上升到故障中值 4062637 微秒。\n   \n2. **node 资源**\n    - `aiops-k8s-04` 的 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 从 9412222976.0 降至 5883379712.0。\n    - `aiops-k8s-04` 的 `node_memory_usage_rate` 从 42.49% 上升至 63.53% 。\n\n### 假设验证\n假设根因可能是 `checkoutservice` 服务性能的劣化和 `aiops-k8s-04` 节点内存使用异常。\n\n### 支持与否\n由于 `checkoutservice` 服务的异常指标较为突出，尤其是错误率和最大响应时间的显著上升，即便 `aiops-k8s-04` 节点存在内存使用的变化，这种变化没有达到绝对显著的程度以至于成为主要根因。因此，应当：\n- 偏向于认为 `checkoutservice` 服务异常是主要问题。\n- `aiops-k8s-04` 的内存问题可能对某些 Pod 的性能造成了一定影响，但不是主要因素。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"OPPOSE\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Abnormal increase in error_ratio and rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"The error_ratio rose from 0.0 to 25.98 and rrt_max from 162292 to 4062637\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Moderate increase in node_memory_usage_rate\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Node memory usage rate rose from 42.49% to 63.53%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "checkoutservice is the root cause due to DNS lookup failure and server misbehaving issues, leading to significant delays and connection errors with emailservice."}
